TDistinctCompare = enum
  dcEq,                     ## a and b should be the same type
  dcEqIgnoreDistinct,       ## compare symmetrically: (distinct a) == b, a == b
                             ## or a == (distinct b)
  dcEqOrDistinctOf           ## a equals b or a is distinct of b
